metadata.name: BAND Royalty Series 1: Double Diamond Album #0001/3000 Every Time It’s Played
metadata.description: BAND Royalty is your entrance into the music industry matrix, where we celebrate the diversity of music worldwide with beautifully curated limited-edition artwork, creating a truly inclusive platform that lets music lovers and fans take their enjoyment to the next level by offering blockchain-secured BAND Royalty NFTs that enable holders who stake their NFTs onto the BAND Royalty platform with the potential to earn crypto from some of the world’s most popular songs and artists. In this BAND Royalty Series 1 there is a maximum supply of 3000 NFTs.
metadata.author: BAND Royalty
